	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You hold a yew leaf as you chant a short spell. You gain the ability to sense poisons and diseases, usually by amplifying visual or olfactory cues that a creature or object is contaminated.</em></p><p><strong>Ritual Casting Time:</strong> 1 Minute</p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>You can sense the presence and location of poisons, poisonous creatures, diseases, and creatures afflicted with a poison or a disease within 30 feet of you. The spell can penetrate most barriers, but it is blocked by 1 foot of stone, 1 inch of common metal, a thin sheet of lead, or 3 feet of wood or dirt.</p></li></ul>",
			"chat": ""
		},
